data.description: BACK ON MARKET, DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER. BUYERS FINANCING FELL THROUGH... This 3-bedroom 2 bath home sits in a peaceful neighborhood that has the feel of a county like setting. Located in Bolivar and only 20 minutes from Stockon lake and about 30 minutes from Pom de Terre. The unique light fixtures throughout the home add character to this very spacious home. It also has a sunroom that could be used as an office. The master bath has a jetted tub. The backyard is set up for entertaining and is mostly surrounded with a privacy fence. It also has a nice sized storage shed for those extras. The kitchen has two dining areas and a great space for a coffee nook.  So many possibilities.  Call for your tour today!
